    2 C      -2.119   -3.919   -0.038   -2.216   -3.733    0.050   -2.131   -3.768    0.101    0.139
    3 Br    -27.935   -6.806    0.259  -27.976   -6.852    0.172  -27.932   -6.926    0.142   -0.118
    4 O      -3.214   -4.943   -0.158   -3.430   -4.730   -0.159   -3.243   -5.083   -0.327   -0.169
    5 H      -0.092   -1.434   -0.526   -0.116   -1.277   -0.392   -0.131   -1.315   -0.446    0.081
    6 H      -0.093   -1.485   -0.578   -0.117   -1.318   -0.434   -0.132   -1.378   -0.510    0.068
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Total NetCharge:               0.000                      0.000                      0.000   -0.000
 (accuracy NumInt/Tails)

    e) the SCF spin density

  Atom                  SCF
             Sphere RestCell NetTotal
 -------     ------------------------
    1 C       0.043    0.561    0.604
    2 C      -0.003    0.016    0.013
    3 Br      0.005    0.060    0.065
    4 O       0.050    0.145    0.196
